@startuml
skinparam backgroundColor #FFFFFF
skinparam roundCorner 15
skinparam ArrowColor #555555
[*] --> Closed
Closed --> Pending : process
Closed : entry / log shipment
Pending --> Draft : update
Draft --> Completed : reject
Draft : entry / log shipment
Completed --> Reviewed : submit
Reviewed --> Rejected : confirm
Rejected --> Draft : revert
Rejected --> [*]
@enduml